Hello everyone.  I have recently acquired a few more T210 Series 6 cards and I have the following cards

1. Goostree with Bat Winchester: SGC A
2. Toney Winchester
3. Callahan Winchester
4. Scherenberg Paris Portrait Variation

I focus on Winchester but there are a few cards I have searched in vain for that I would like to get.  My wantlist includes

1.Creager Richmond
2.Viox Lexington
3.Vanlandingham either team variation
4.Any Frankfort Player or other Winchester Players

The only card I do not want to trade from my list above is the Toney card. The others I will be happy to consider a trade for.  If anyone is intersted in trading for any of these please email me at [url]wacturner@hotmail.com[/url]  
As always if anyone has anything from my wantlist for sale also please contact me also.  Hope to here from a few fellow T210 collectors.  If you have some series 6 cards that are not on my want list feel free to contact me anyway through the board or at my email listed above and I will be happy to discuss it.  Thanks

William
